### State Machine — Request Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DRAFT: User mulai isi form
    DRAFT --> PENDING_MANAGER: User submit + sign
    PENDING_MANAGER --> PENDING_ICT: Manager approve + sign
    PENDING_MANAGER --> REJECTED: Manager reject
    PENDING_ICT --> CONFIRMED: ICT confirm + provision credentials
    PENDING_ICT --> REJECTED: ICT reject
    CONFIRMED --> [*]: User view credentials
    REJECTED --> [*]: User notified
```

