## Architecture Diagram — End-to-End Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Requester)
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant BE as Backend (NestJS)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant NS as Notification Service
    participant M as Manager
    participant ICT as ICT Agent

    U->>FE: 1. Select "Form VPN"
    FE->>FE: 2. Multi-step wizard form
    U->>FE: 3. Fill form + Sign + Select Manager
    FE->>BE: POST /eform-request (formData + signature + managerId)
    BE->>DB: INSERT eform_requests (status=PENDING_MANAGER)
    BE->>DB: INSERT eform_signatures (requester)
    BE->>DB: INSERT eform_approvals (sequence=1 APPROVED, sequence=2 PENDING)
    BE->>NS: emit('eform.submitted')
    NS->>M: 4. Notification: "New VPN request pending your approval"

    M->>FE: 5. Open request detail
    FE->>BE: GET /eform-request/:id
    BE-->>FE: Return full form + signatures
    M->>FE: 6. Review + Sign + Approve
    FE->>BE: PATCH /eform-request/:id/manager-approve (signature)
    BE->>DB: UPDATE status=PENDING_ICT
    BE->>DB: INSERT eform_signatures (manager)
    BE->>NS: emit('eform.manager-approved')
    NS->>ICT: 7. Notification: "VPN request approved, pending provisioning"
    NS->>U: Notification: "Your request was approved by manager"

    ICT->>FE: 8. Open request detail
    FE->>BE: GET /eform-request/:id
    ICT->>FE: 9. Input credentials + Sign + Confirm
    FE->>BE: PATCH /eform-request/:id/ict-confirm (signature)
    FE->>BE: POST /eform-request/:id/credentials (username, password)
    BE->>BE: 🔐 AES-256-GCM Encrypt(credentials)
    BE->>DB: INSERT eform_credentials (encrypted)
    BE->>DB: UPDATE status=CONFIRMED
    BE->>NS: emit('eform.credentials-provisioned')
    NS->>U: 10. Notification: "Your VPN access is ready!"

    U->>FE: 11. Open request detail
    FE->>BE: GET /eform-request/:id/credentials
    BE->>BE: Verify req.user.id === requesterId
    BE->>BE: 🔓 AES-256-GCM Decrypt(credentials)
    BE-->>FE: Return plaintext username + password
    FE->>FE: 12. Display in CredentialViewer (60s auto-hide)
```
